                    <span>I picked this book up as a gift for someone who has talked about traveling to visit all ballparks over the next few years.  Enjoyed reading about some of the ballparks that I have recently visited, but was disappointed to see that while this book was reveised in 2001, he did not visit BOB in Phoenix.  The information is all pre-opening and is even written as if the park is not yet opened.   Good discriptions of Pac-Bell and Safco field both which opened after BOB.</span>
                  
